# Student Admin System â€” C Program

A simple terminal-based student management system written in C. It allows you to add, list, search, and delete student records stored in a binary file.

---

## Features

- Add new student with ID, Name, Course, and GPA  
- List all students in a formatted table  
- Search student by ID  
- Delete student record safely using a temp file  
- Data stored persistently in `student_records.dat`

